entries.femaleVariant: Hi! How is everybody! Got some news with some spice. Lizzy Wizzy has just released her first BD. Yes, THAT Lizzy Wizzy!
It's called "Frac-sure Enough" and in it she lays bare her heartbreaking split with Liam Northom.
At first, Lizzy and Northom looked like the perfect pair... But then their little slice of heaven started to grow mold.
"Frac-sure Enough" is a tumultuous journey through the superstar's sadness, disappointment, pain... and then the ecstasy when she exacts her revenge.
When you feel Northom's body fall limp in your hands, with his hot blood streaking down your chrome skin... I mean, wow! Preem catharsis!
"Frac-sure enough" is a braindance masterpiece and proof that Lizzy Wizzy's genius extends far, far beyond her music.
I cannot recommend it enough! "Frac-sure Enough" by the one and only Lizzy Wizzy is available on feeders now! Check it out!
